params.consumer: - New consumer which can use the subscription

cancelSubscription(uint64,address).details: Only callable by the Subscription's owner

params.to: - Where to send the remaining LINK to

createSubscriptionWithConsumer(address).details: You can manage the consumer set dynamically with addConsumer/removeConsumer.Note to fund the subscription, use transferAndCall. For exampleLINKTOKEN.transferAndCall(address(ROUTER),amount,abi.encode(subscriptionId));

params.subscriptionIdStart: - the ID of the subscription to start the range at

returns._0: subscriptions - see IFunctionsSubscriptions.Subscription for more information on the structure
totalBalance - total Juels of LINK held by the contract

returns._0: true if there exists at least one unfulfilled request for the subscription, false otherwise.
